<div class="flex flex-col h-full">

  <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-mono mb-3">Hello, I'm</p>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">
      Walter Frias
    </h1>

    <h2 class="text-base text-slate-400 font-medium mb-6 leading-snug">
      Full Stack Developer<br />
      Python · TypeScript · Solidity
    </h2>

    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs mb-16">
      Building web2 products and web3 protocols. I bring a visual arts
      background to every interface I craft.
    </p>

